Specialized care 3 For pregnant women with type 1 or type 2 diabetes, deliver multidisciplinary and
specialized care provided by health-care providers trained in maternal and diabetes care.
4 For women with GDM, consider multidisciplinary and specialized care provided by health-
care providers trained in maternal and diabetes care, depending on access and availability.
